ygData.messageBody:
Don't try dagnor's for quite a long time, until at least 16, and then only grouped. Right now, I reccomend you either stay at the chessboard or go to the dragon bones in Steamfont, which in my opinion is the best place to fight at level 10.

Sloop, Holy Enchanter of Fennin Ro
